16
00:01:09.278 --> 00:01:12.823
<i>He was killed in the ensuing brawl.
The fan was later beaten to death...</i>

17
00:01:12.906 --> 00:01:14.074
Coffee. please. Black.

18
00:01:14.157 --> 00:01:15.492
<i>By the angry crowd.</i>

19
00:01:15.617 --> 00:01:20.247
<i>Born in 2009.
the son of Marcello and Sylvia Ricardo.</i>

20
00:01:20.330 --> 00:01:22.833
<i>a working-class couple from Mendoza.</i>

21
00:01:23.083 --> 00:01:26.336
