00:37:27.706 --> 00:37:30.876
<i>Fishes terrorist leader Julian Taylor
was killed today</i>

488
00:37:30.959 --> 00:37:33.504
<i>in a gun battle with
police near Canterbury.</i>

489
00:37:33.712 --> 00:37:38.008
