527
00:39:03.427 --> 00:39:04.595
A wanted fugee.

528
00:39:04.636 --> 00:39:07.764
Why don't we explain to Mr. Faron
what they do to immigrants in this country?

529
00:39:07.806 --> 00:39:10.809
