536
00:39:27.618 --> 00:39:28.952
And when you and the baby
are well enough.

537
00:39:28.994 --> 00:39:31.246
we will find a way
to get you to the Human Project.

538
00:39:31.330 --> 00:39:32.330
I promise you. Kee.

539
00:39:32.372 --> 00:39:35.626
